com.diffplug.common.rx

Interface GuardedExecutor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Executor, RxSubscriber
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GuardedExecutor.AbstractGuardedExecutor

    public interface GuardedExecutor
extends Executor, RxSubscriber
    GuardedExecutor is an Executor and RxSubscriber which promises to cancel its subscriptions and stop executing tasks once its guard() has been disposed. Useful for tying asynchronous tasks to gui elements.
